quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  28,36,"Nde Muusaa addunoo e ma…ď…ďe aayeeje Amen …óen …ďanngu…óe, …ďe mbi'i: "∆äum wonaani, si wonaa mbilewu fekindaangu. Min naniraani …óum baabiraa…ďe amen adinoo…ďe …ďen"."
  28,37,"Muusaa maaki: "Ko Joomi am …ďuri anndude on ardu…óo e peewal, immorde to makko, e on mo battane mo∆ī∆īe woodani ka La'akara. Pellet, O malnataa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"."
  28,38,"Fir'awna wi'i: "eey mon dental, mi anndanaa on dewetee…óo, si wonaa min. Eey ma yo Haamaana, hu…ď…ďinanam [yiite] e loopal ngal, mahiranaa kam hu…ďeere toownde, no gasa ka mi ∆īellitoo e Dewetee…óo Muusaa On; tawde mi…óo sikki mo e fenoo…ďe …ďen"."
  28,39,"O townitii ka leydi, kaŇčko e koneeli makko …óin, ko aldaa e goonga. ∆Āe cikki won'de …ďe ruttitetaako ka Amen."
  28,40,"Men nanngi mo, kaŇčko e koneeli makko …óin, Min mbugii …ďe ka maayo. Tasko, ko honno battane too√Ī…ďe …ďen mba'unoo."
  28,41,"Min mba…ói …ďe ardii…ďe, noddoo …ďe e Yiite. √Ďande Darngal, …ďe walletaake."
  28,42,"Min njokkintiniri …ďe ka aduna …óoo, kuddi. √Ďalnde Darngal, ko …ďe jiyaa…ďe e wo…ó…óintinoytee…ďe [e yurmeende Alla]."
  28,43,"GooŇč…óii Min ngokkii Muusaa Deftere nden, …ďaawo nde Min kalkunoo gire arane …óen, ko nde ndayginorde yim…ďe …ďen, e peewal e yurmeende. Mbelejo'o, …ďe mbaajitorat."